description: While some sources consider this name to be a synonym for Salicional, most define it as a Salicional of 4' or 2' pitch. Over half the known examples are at 4' pitch.
examplesDescription: Osiris contains 39 examples at 4' pitch, ten at 8' pitch, seven at 16', and six at 2'. The earliest ones are listed below.

examples.name: Salicet 8', Hauptwerk; Abbey, Ottobeuren, Germany; Riepp 1766.
Salicet 8', Oberwerk; Abbey Church, Neresheim, Germany; Holzhay 1797.
Salicet 4', Oberwerk; Jacobikirche, Dornburg, Thuringia, Germany; Gerhardt 1820.
